{"tid":1185532,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"用緊xt20 好頹","createTime":"2019-06-04T10:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:40:54.000Z","uid":165499,"like":4,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9005e36f058d92f3531376319525fdc9f9717b8c","tid":1185532,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:16:00.000Z","msg":"我新手同埋都唔高要求 平時都無影開相 諗住買部機玩下 <br />\n咁就買左xt20 做旅行機 志在玩下咁<br />\n有時搞一輪影出黎仲衰過iphone影<br />\n黑位太黑 搞下iso 又曝哂光咁<br />\n有時auto setting影出黎都無iPhone影咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用到好頹 <br />\n歐洲好多時都天氣差 有時拎相機搞一輪仲衰過iphone 9影.......<br />\n<br />\n但遠少少既野 iphone攝影能力有限 所以都覺得有部相機好<br />\n<br />\nFuji唔岩我？ 轉會 會唔會 對我好d?<br />\n有無d機係鳩影都靚？<br />\n筆直1萬內啦 愈平愈好 見到canon m50 4000蚊有 又想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ba9840b4190b9f50e47099fb57afb5d6fc2a65","tid":1185532,"uid":21751,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"學下點影相先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419606c5790adc271a32439b4f257d6e466b2f5e","tid":1185532,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"any sample shots?"},{"pid":"1fc7fe39b0ab002bbe0d02003237ef64fcb4571b","tid":1185532,"uid":47952,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"唔好好去學下設定影相 <br />\n十萬蚊買部機都係覺得唔夠手機靚"},{"pid":"cb807eb4ed448384729cc64fcb7fb3ce23ba003b","tid":1185532,"uid":136023,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"睇你應該係唔啱用專業少少嘅機影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議考慮買部影相靚嘅電話算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相機有哂測光 xt20又有曝光補償嘅轉盤 都仲可以唔識曝光嘅嘅話 建議賣返出去唔好哂咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個唔係機問題<br />\n係用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da73a083a378fc9653491b8e875e501b041ad00e","tid":1185532,"uid":136023,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">黑位太黑 搞下iso 又曝哂光咁<br />\n有時auto setting影出黎都無iPhone影咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算畀你買多幾部又點<br />\n點曝光都唔識曝 買幾多部都係一樣結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係有心想影靚相就唔好懶 認認真真去學吓點影相<br />\n如果唔係你只係浪費咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9506222bb37916c6c96cb226e3c67142c85b23c","tid":1185532,"uid":11382,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"點用部機都唔識，比部a9你都死啦"},{"pid":"7c44fccca16e22b30c053e849ca4b9691cb3a123","tid":1185532,"uid":43768,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"fuji 直出DR 差，暗位易死黑是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過你技術不足都係主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129f7f51d781e64005be3445a6143eebc800338d","tid":1185532,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"手機影相其實幾神，阿豬阿狗都舞得掂測光/對焦"},{"pid":"fba089e8294946301bdb688560927c2cd682c6ad","tid":1185532,"uid":71341,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dfbaa91f0892fa5fcf2f26a5e56e246e22b2e0b","tid":1185532,"uid":204796,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"XT20 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ah5GkEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fah5GkEQ.jpg&h=47ebd45b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqmaYrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqmaYrw.jpg&h=886dd8c3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.c